Package com.att.research.xacml.std.trace

Provides standard implementations of the interfaces defined in the com.att.research.xacml.api.trace package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LoggingTraceEngine
    Implements the TraceEngine interface to log TraceEvents using the Apache Commons logging system with debug messages.
    LoggingTraceEngineFactory
    Extends the TraceEngineFactory class to implement the getTraceEngine method to return an instance of the LoggingTraceEngine class.
    NullTraceEngine
    Implements the TraceEngine interface to just ignore TraceEvents.
    NullTraceEngineFactory
    Extends the TraceEngineFactory class to implement the getTraceEngine method to return an instance of the NullTraceEngine class.
    StdTraceEvent<T>
    Immutable implementation of the TraceEvent interface.
